{"tid":729194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【支付渠道】港人最愛畀cash同八達通！手機支付排尾三","createTime":"2018-07-04T10:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-04T11:57:28.000Z","uid":12599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7d8e45a67a2d67094ddd9b76a40747f041aee02e","tid":729194,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:50:09.000Z","msg":"調查發現，過去一年市民最常用支付渠道中，現金及八達通分別佔99%及97%，手機支付則只有20%，排名尾三，並落後內地的98%及瑞典的60%。生產力局總經理（資訊科技）黃家偉表示，「如果香港唔做（智慧支付），就會流失部分客源。」<br />\n<br />\n生產促進局發佈「Alipay HK智慧支付普及指數」調查，訪問了400間零售企業及1000名市民，普及指數為53.9（數字愈高代表愈普及），其中商家及用家得分分別為62.2及45.5，反映商家智慧支付準備程度較高。<br />\n<br />\n若按零售業務分類，珠寶首飾、鐘錶及名貴禮物得分最高，為73.7，其餘介乎56.5至66.3之間。黃家偉解釋，該行業本來少收現金，加上現時多內地客人，本已習慣手機支付。<br />\n<br />\n港人過去一年最常用的支付渠道中，依次為現金、八達通、信用卡簽賬，EPS、接觸式信用卡、手機支付、網上付費及商店預付會員卡。<br />\n<br />\n調查又發現，用家用對智慧支付接受程度偏低，得分僅45.5，低過50分界線，主要因為不了解相關操作及擔心私隱外洩，更有近5成人滿意現時支付模式。對於會否再「燒錢」推廣，Alipay HK行政總裁陳婉真表示，折扣優惠明顯不是港人使用智慧支付的原因，「新brand開頭可能推優惠，但消費者好精明，要易用好用先會用」。<br />\n<br />\n記者：張浚浩<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180704/58398050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180704%2F58398050&d=hcKOE3i8VJxvkOAuUfaprcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e2a6361b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180704%2F58398050&h=9ecd33fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180704/58398050</a>"},{"pid":"43f290fcd526fd6da3db20bbcb94956cb74b07d4","tid":729194,"uid":58335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T10:59:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">折扣優惠明顯不是港人使用智慧支付的原因</span><br />\n<br />\n香港人最撚貪小便宜<br />\n定位都未知<br />\n返上去支那啦"},{"pid":"21a686ae4192fcb1864ddca9f21ddf6f48c1d7e2","tid":729194,"uid":7628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"八達通自動增值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用乜鳩支那寶"},{"pid":"2e645e9bffc501e507e9569100c2fc7d4f0a4573","tid":729194,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21a686ae4192fcb1864ddca9f21ddf6f48c1d7e2","tid":729194,"uid":7628,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"八達通自動增值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用乜鳩支那寶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:12:08.000Z","msg":"底層一個用credit card, 一個大部份用debit card<br />\n<br />\n原因你懂的<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f21cc1a627db9b87f10f5525480d68498362cc","tid":729194,"uid":4964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:15:00.000Z","msg":"paywave仲少人用過EPS?"},{"pid":"5c500dd3049a49b8a3146ea26f0b43422ae05ffb","tid":729194,"uid":69797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"我想問 點樣可以分別佔 99％ 97％？"},{"pid":"ca28475c13065b1c41e5d913a6850a1cb223902d","tid":729194,"uid":69797,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-04T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"利申 我明佢講乜的 但d中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}